About The Windjammer Always a Jam Good Time! Located at Front Beach on the Isle of Palms, The Windjammer is Charleston's premier live music beach venue for over the last 50 years. From local bands to big name artists, guests can enjoy the best in live music. The Windjammer also offers delicious beach eats with menu items including buffalo chicken wings, cheeseburgers, fish & chips, and more. Relax and sip on a cold beer or refreshing cocktail while taking in the unbeatable beach views. The Windjammer where, it's always a JAM good time!
